description: Amazing opportunity to own this beautiful Fort Point, BPDA income restricted condo! Income Restrictions Apply: Maximum income of $211,475 for 1-2 person household. Buyer's total assets (exclusive of retirement accounts) cannot exceed $100,000. This exposed brick and beam, open concept condo will not disappoint! The gorgeous kitchen is recently updated with custom cabinetry, quartz counter tops, tiled backsplash and stainless steel appliances package, which includes a gas range.  There are stunning wide plank maple hardwood floors and 12 ' ceilings that have been professionally sound proofed between the beams.  All this plus washer/dryer hook-ups in the unit, custom wardrobe storage, central heat and A/C!  Not to mention LOW condo fees of just $258/month. Fort Point is a prime location that is close to the Seaport, Downtown, airport and South Station public transportation.
